#################################################################################
#
# When we play a .wav file, the time taken to complete playback should be very
# close to the length of the track.
#
#################################################################################
@core_regression
Feature: Playback Timing
    We should be able to play a .wav file and not have it take significantly
    longer than the length of the .wav.

    ###########################################################################
    #
    # Play a test sound and verify the time taken against the length.
    #
    ###########################################################################
    @hw_setup_tests
    Scenario: Playback time and track length should match
        When I play the audio file "resources/test.wav"
        Then the time taken is within 1.5 s of the length of "resources/test.wav"

